data.title: Nia Long Net Worth - One Of The Richest Women In Hollywood Today
data.meta_description: American actress, video artist, TV personality, and inspiration Nia Long (born Nia Talita Long) is known by her stage name Nia. Nia Long net worth is $6 million by the year 2022. She has been nominated for several honors for her cinematic work, including Black reel awards and NAACP Image awards.
